## Optimization Summary for Q2 Iteration 10

### Bottleneck Analysis
From execution_results.json (iteration 1), the dominant bottleneck is:
- **`compute_min_costs`: 172.32 ms (60.5% of total 284.94 ms)** - a serial scan of 8M partsupp rows
